dents Now and Transform Marginalized Communities Tomorrow.      Your gifts to our Student Emergency Fund and Student Scholarship Fund provide support now as our students deal with the financial hardships of COVID-19 and the costs associated with higher education. But the impact of your gift continues into the future as our graduates apply the knowledge and skills they gain to create a more equitable society and transform marginalized communities.      Give to the Fund(s) of Your Choice:       UIC Jane Addams College of Social Work Student Emergency Fund   $          UIC Jane Addams College of Social Work Scholarship Fund   $          Jane Addams College of Social Work Annual Fund   $          UIC Professor James P. Gleeson Scholarship Fund   $          UIC Jane Addams Class of 1973 Scholarship Fund   $          UIC Class of 1990 Scholarship Fund   $          UIC Jane Addams Center for Social Policy and Research Fund   $                Alumni & Friends    Back to main content           Make a Gift Now    IGNITE Campaign: Make Your Impact    Where & How to Give    Connect & Engage     Update Your Information    What's New With You?    Engage With Students    Alumni & Friends Newsletter      Alumni Events & Awards     Award Nominations      Alumni Updates    LSW/LCSW Information              Jane Addams College of Social Work  UI Health                        UIC's seven health sciences colleges and health care delivery enterprise.       Footer Menu 4    For Prospective Students    Apply Now    Alumni & Friends    Make a Gift Now    Current Students & Faculty         Contact   MSW Admissions  1040 West Harrison Street (MC309), Chicago, Illinois 60607-7134  jaddams-msw@uic.edu    PhD Admissions  1040 West Harrison Street (MC309), Chicago, Illinois 60607-7134  jcswphd@uic.edu      Social Media Accounts    Facebook    LinkedIn    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emerg